# Profit Or Loss Non Current Assets Disposal Groups Held For Sale Not Discontinued Operation Gains Amount

## identifier
de13812

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, during the relevant period, for any gains on the measurement of non-current assets (or disposal groups); classified as held for sale that does not meet the definition of discontinued operation. This item must be reported in accordance with the relevant accounting standard.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=ProfitOrLoss.NonCurrentAssetsDisposalGroupsHeldForSaleNotDiscontinuedOperationGains.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.19
- period=duration
